OL,3,CBody parts search continues after
OL,4,Cwoman's remains found in park
OL,6,FPolice are continuing to search for
OL,7,Fbody parts after a woman was allegedly
OL,8,Fmurdered, cut up with power tools and
OL,9,Fdumped in a park near Croydon.
OL,11,FRemains belonging to Sarah Mayhew, 38,
OL,12,Fwere found in Rowdown Fields in New
OL,13,FAddington, south London, after police
OL,14,Fwere called last Tuesday morning.
OL,16,FGemma Watts, 48, and Steven Sansom,
OL,17,F44, were arrested on Saturday and
OL,18,Fsubsequently charged with her murder
OL,19,Fand preventing her lawful and decent
OL,20,Fburial.
