OL,6,FOn Thursday, the couple were due to
OL,7,Fappear at the Old Bailey before Judge
OL,8,FPhilip Katz KC.
OL,10,FWatts, of Featherbed Lane in New
OL,11,FAddington, appeared first by video
OL,12,Flink from Bronzefield prison.
OL,14,FShe appeared to have a dark bruise
OL,15,Faround her eye and spoke only to
OL,16,Fconfirm her identity.
OL,18,FThe court heard that both she and
OL,19,FSansom are alleged to have killed Ms
OL,20,FMayhew at a residential property on
OL,21,Fthe night of March 8.
