OL,3,CBody parts search continues after
OL,4,Cwoman's remains found in park
OL,6,FAfterwards, prosecutors claim Ms
OL,7,FMayhew's body was cut up with power
OL,8,Ftools and disposed of.
OL,10,FProsecutor Tom Little KC said there
OL,11,Fwas an "ongoing investigation in
OL,12,Frelation to the whereabouts of the
OL,13,Fentirety of the deceased's body".
OL,15,F"The deceased's body was certainly cut
OL,16,Fup in parts with use of power tools,"
OL,17,Fhe added.
OL,19,FJudge Katz set a plea hearing for June
OL,20,F27 and a provisional four-week trial
OL,21,Ffrom February 17 next year.
