OL,6,FThe Old Bailey judge remanded Watts
OL,7,Finto custody.
OL,9,FThe court was told that Sansom, of
OL,10,FBurnell Road, Sutton, south-west
OL,11,FLondon, will appear at the same court
OL,12,Fat 2pm.
OL,14,FHe also faces three separate charges
OL,15,Fof making indecent images of a child.
